<p>And the retailer, which is best known for its very affordable everyday items, has continued to win over its shoppers by dropping hidden gems in its homeware aisles.</p>

<p>Thousands of customers are flocking to the one-stop-shop for all their modern home décor, storage solutions and on-trend furniture pieces.</p>

